name: Pulsation in Deep Mauve
description:
Get these beautiful cases for your iPad and mobile phone!

Designed by artist Jenny Bhatt, each design features an image of her painting. 

An individualistic way to accessorize your devices with a one-piece, hard case featuring a slim profile. This is a one-time special offer of buying 2 pieces of the same design.

Available for iPad, iPhone, Samsung, Blackberry and Nokia Lumia.
Email your device specifications to order.
